Ranger Help for: quickshot
==========================

SYNTAX:      quickshot <target> or qshot <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   6
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  bow

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to fire a rapid volley of arrows at a
target. The Ranger sacrifices accuracy for speed, firing multiple
shots in quick succession. Each individual hit does less damage than
a carefully aimed shot, but the combined effect of multiple arrows
can be devastating. The number of arrows fired depends on the
Ranger's dexterity and proficiency with the skill.
